OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom contacting couple     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former BBC radio presenter in jail   
OL,6, for stalking has been banned from      
OL,7, contacting two more people.            
OL,9,FAlex Belfield, 43, who is serving a    
OL,10,Ffive-and-a-half year sentence for      
OL,11,Fharassing four people online, including
OL,12,Fbroadcaster Jeremy Vine, was made the  
OL,13,Fsubject of a stalking protection order.
OL,15,FHe is banned from attempting to contact
OL,16,FGreg Scott, a man he sent a tweet to,  
OL,17,Fand his wife Karen.                    
OL,19,FHe may also not publish, or attempt to,
OL,20,Fmaterial relating to them.             
